data.event: The last ship launched by Goshen shipyard was the “Diamond” in 1898.
The Tavern House (circa 1725), located on the corner of Route 47 and Goshen Landing Road is one of the oldest original homes in Cape May County.
While significant changes were made over the years, much of the original workmanship is still evident.
